data.description: This 3/2/2 home is it! Stepping into this home you are greeted with a cozy living room with is carpeted. The dining room leads into the kitchen where you have a dishwasher, built-in microwave, breakfast bar, and a double sink. The master bedroom has its own bathroom which is equipped with a separate shower, and separate tub. The guest bathroom is a tub/shower combo. There is a shed in the back. The garage door and garage door opener is new, as well as new faucets, tub, and shower. The garage which is located in the side/rear of the home is a double car and is attached. Located in the Lubbock ISD school district. Come and see this home before it is too late.
